2.0 Installation and testing

To compile the library start terminal go to the directory where HHFFT is uncompressed and type:

mkdir bin
cd bin
cmake ..
make

To specify where the library should be installed use
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path/where/to/put/hhfft .. 
instead of just cmake ..

If you want to install the compiled library run
sudo make install

To test that the compilation has been succesful, run the test1
./hhfft_test1

on the last line of the output should read "Test passed!"


3.0 Linking library to your project

To link with HHFFT use -lhhfft flag in compiler.
If the library is not found when running the program try to call:
sudo ldconfig

